# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# math.ese — 算学词库 / Mathematical Vocabulary
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# Classical Chinese mathematical operations.
# These are the most fundamental — 4-character programs for math.
#
#   加三于四  → 7   (add three to four)
#   三加四    → 7   (three add four — word-order variant)
#   三乘四    → 12  (three multiply four)
#   一至十合  → 55  (one to ten sum — Gauss's formula)
#   以 R0 为七 → R0 = 7  (take register zero as seven)
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Domain declaration ──────────────────────────────────────
@domain: 算 (mathematics)
@description: 算学词库 — 文言数学运算

# ── Arithmetic operators ────────────────────────────────────
加 → IADD         # Add
减 → ISUB         # Subtract
乘 → IMUL         # Multiply
除 → IDIV         # Divide
余 → IMOD         # Modulo
幂 → IEXP         # Power
根 → IROOT        # Square root

# ── Comparison operators ────────────────────────────────────
等 → IEQ          # Equal
大于 → IGT        # Greater than
小于 → ILT        # Less than
非零 → INZ        # Not zero

# ── Accumulation ────────────────────────────────────────────
合 → ISUM         # Sum / combine
积 → IPROD        # Product
至 → RANGE        # Range (to)
遍 → EACH         # For each / iterate

# ── Special values ──────────────────────────────────────────
零 → 0            # Zero
一 → 1            # One (also: true)
无 → NULL         # Nothing / null
全 → ALL          # Everything / all
极 → MAX          # Ultimate / maximum

# ── Classical patterns ─────────────────────────────────────
# 天元术 → ALGEBRA  (Song dynasty polynomial method)
# 方程    → EQUATION (Nine Chapters method)
# 勾股    → PYTHAGORAS (right triangle)
# 割圆    → PI_APPROXIMATION (Liu Hui's circle method)
